              <span id="reviewTextContainer110470981" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7393148067977856274">Many people today view the cross as a religious symbol that represents the crucifixion (pain, suffering, and death) of Jesus. Nwaocha Ogechukwu’s “The Secret Behind the Cross and Crucifix,” explains how the cross has been misrepresented. This book explains how the cross was initially used in satanic practices before the Christian Era and it also defines and describes the many different types of crosses. This book also explains the role the cross has played in paganism and idolatry. There is no d</span>
  <span id="freeText7393148067977856274" style="display:none">Many people today view the cross as a religious symbol that represents the crucifixion (pain, suffering, and death) of Jesus. Nwaocha Ogechukwu’s “The Secret Behind the Cross and Crucifix,” explains how the cross has been misrepresented. This book explains how the cross was initially used in satanic practices before the Christian Era and it also defines and describes the many different types of crosses. This book also explains the role the cross has played in paganism and idolatry. There is no doubt that Jesus was crucified, but for those who have a question about the cross and the crucifixion, “The Secret Behind the Cross and Crucifix,” is a must read!</span>
